OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother largely dry and fine
OL,6,Fday with plenty of sunshine. Feeling a
OL,7,Flittle fresher than on Tuesday, with
OL,8,Fan easterly breeze, but still very
OL,9,Fwarm. Chance of an isolated shower
OL,10,Flate afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining dry for most,
OL,13,Fhowever an area of showers will push
OL,14,Fnorth and eastwards across the region
OL,15,Fovernight. Cooler than recent nights.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FA few scattered showers
OL,18,Finitially on Thursday, but these will
OL,19,Fsoon clear. Leaving most places dry
OL,20,Fand settled with plenty of sunshine on
OL,21,Foffer. Feeling very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
