OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,6,Flargely fine and settled over the
OL,7,Fcoming days, however it will turn
OL,8,Fcloudier from the west at times, with
OL,9,Fan increasing chance of rain,
OL,10,Fparticularly Saturday. Temperatures
OL,11,Fnear normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
